msg: Added support for controlling properties for well-known environments. The "vmassol" one is the one I'm setting up at home to generate nightly builds of Cactus (to replace Gump which is not currently working)

author: vmassol
msg: - Refactoring: Transformed o.a.c.WebRequest from a class to an interface. This breaks the binary compatibility in the hope of helping preserve it in the future... :-)

- During the refactoring I had to introduce a WebRequestImpl class. Until now we haven't used this notation of <interface name>Impl. I couldn't find a nice name. If anyone has a better idea please put it forward!
